  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK514">
<l>eṉaivakaiyāṟ ṟēṟiyak kaṇṇum viṉaivakaiyāṉ</l>
<l>vēṟāku māntar palar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even when (a king) has tried them in every possible way, there are many men who change, from the nature of the works (in which they may be employed).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
